  "prompt": "What are Apple's vision and mission statements?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, Apple's mission statement is often summarized as \"to bring the best user experience to its customers through its innovative products.\" This focuses on delivering high-quality technology and software that enhance the lives of users.\n\nApple's vision statement expresses a commitment to innovation and leadership in technology while emphasizing environmental responsibility and making an impact in the world. It typically revolves around revolutionizing how technology integrates into daily life and ensuring sustainability.\n\nHowever, it's important to note that companies may revise their vision and mission statements from time to time, so for the most current and specific wording, checking Apple's official website or their latest corporate communications would be advisable.",
